bXBvcmFyeS1hZnJpY2FuLWFydD91dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249V2FsbCtQb3dlcistK1NVQlNDUklCRVJ=
TKyUyODEyJTJGMTAlMkYyNCUyOVx1MDAyNnV0bV9jb250ZW50PVdhbGwrUG93ZXIrLStTVUJTQ1=
JJQkVSUyslMjgxMiUyRjEwJTJGMjQlMjlcdTAwMjZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsX2FjdGlvblx1M=
DAyNnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9Y3VzdG9tZXIuaW9cdTAwMjZ1dG1fdGVybT1mNmM2MDYxN2RhNDJhYmQx=
MmEiLCJpbnRlcm5hbCI6ImY2YzYwNjE3ZGE0MmFiZDEyYSIsImxpbmtfaWQiOjIwMTQxODV9/85=
90e4b534158f6cffca079f64ea0c1d4f1bf1baad7e758fccd9d8a142c51dd7" style=3D"co=
lor:#d40000;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold" class=3D"sdf">art sale</=
a></u> was just mysteriously removed from the company=E2=80=99s website. It=
 appears that offices around the world have had their staff reduced or will=
 be closed outright. (Sotheby=E2=80=99s declined to comment on individual d=
epartures among their more than 1,800 employees; a rep noted that some of t=
he international office closures had been long-planned.) Christie=E2=80=99s=
 also reduced its staff, as often happens around this time of year, but not=
 at the same scale. <br/><br/>No matter what Sotheby=E2=80=99s is or isn=E2=
=80=99t saying, the belt-tightening appears to be deep and wide and perhaps=
 not coincidentally timed to the arrival of the auction house=E2=80=99s new=
 minority owner: Abu Dhabi=E2=80=99s ADQ sovereign wealth fund, which inves=
ted nearly $1 billion in October. The layoffs may not be a direct
condition of ADQ=E2=80=99s cash infusion, but the stipulations attached to =
the deal may have incentivized the restructuring=E2=80=94even if they also =
potentially threaten majority owner <b>Patrick Drahi</b>=E2=80=99s grip on =
the company. <br/></td>
